            "pathId": 5125660316583407072,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "……よしっ！　いよいよ、今日から学園生活スタートだべ……！",
            "enText": "All righty! Starting today, my life as a Tracen Academy \nstudent finally begins!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 141,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -722283168049835069
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 8740860433484157162
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1410321352516196674,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "あ、そうだっ！\r\nスズカさん、よかったら一緒に登校――",
            "enText": "Oh, that's right! If it's okay with you, Suzuka, \ndo you want to go to school toge—",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 133,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 1914272367494071365
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 7085018068588629387
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6331739875464442228,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "って、もういないっ！？",
            "enText": "She's already gone?!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -4612886789515501382
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -8156335778669565939
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3700550776744047336,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "ジャージがない……ということは、もしかして早朝ランニング？\r\nスズカさん、すっごく早起きなんだぁ～……！",
            "enText": "Her tracksuit's not here, so maybe she went for an \nearly morning run? Wow, she really wakes up early…!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 298,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 3175957236337028602
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -4055413848221342005
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7868608672536745118,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "……『私も行きたいです』って言ったら、\r\nまた一緒に走ってもらえるかな？",
            "enText": "I wonder if she'd let me run with her again if I asked.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 180,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 7104466921012785414
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -8996229931064800303
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9074321339481617355,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "今日、寮に帰ってきたら、勇気出して言ってみようかな……！？\r\nそしたら……えっへへ……！！",
            "enText": "Maybe when she gets back, I'll work up the courage to ask. \nThen afterwards… Hee hee!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 267,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": 8691967473122257308
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8346775629096927667
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8473322748768183126,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "――……はっ！！\r\nいけない、ぼんやりしてたら遅刻しちゃうっ！！",
            "enText": "Ah! I gotta get going! If I keep daydreaming, I'm gonna be late!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": -632660941795687950
